\begin_layout Section
隐函数的求导方法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
一般地,如果变量x和y满足一个方程
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)=0$
\end_inset

,在一定条件下,当
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

取区间内的任一值时,相应地总有满足这方程的唯一的
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

值存在,那么就说方程
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)=0$
\end_inset

在该区间内确定了一个
\series bold
一元隐函数
\series default
.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
类似的,
 由方程
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y,z)=0$
\end_inset

 确定的二元函数
\begin_inset Formula $z=f(x,y)$
\end_inset

称为二元隐函数.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
隐函数示例:
\series bold

\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+y^{2}=1$
\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{3}+y^{3}=6xy$
\end_inset

(
\series default
笛卡尔叶形线)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
把一个隐函数化成显函数,叫做
\series bold
隐函数的显化.
 
\series default
例如从方程
\series bold

\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+y^{2}=1$
\end_inset


\series default
 解出
\begin_inset Formula $y=\sqrt{x^{2}-1}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
但是大部分隐函数是不容易显式话的,
 如笛卡尔叶形线.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
显然,通过将隐函数是式化来求出隐函数的导数是行不通的。

\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
方法一:对确定隐函数的方程两边关于自变量求导
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
求由方程
\begin_inset Formula $e^{x}-e^{y}-xy=0$
\end_inset

 确定的隐函数
\begin_inset Formula $y=f(x)$
\end_inset

 的导数
\begin_inset Formula $y'$
\end_inset

及
\begin_inset Formula $y'(0)$
\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
对方程
\begin_inset Formula $e^{x}-e^{y}-xy=0$
\end_inset

两边关于
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

求导,注意到
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的函数,
 得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
e^{x}-e^{y}y'-(y+xy')=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
便得到隐函数的导数:
\begin_inset Formula $y'=\frac{e^{x}-y}{x+e^{y}}(x+e^{y}\neq0)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution*
又
\begin_inset Formula $x=0$
\end_inset

时,代入原方程得
\begin_inset Formula $y=0$
\end_inset

,于是将
\begin_inset Formula $x=0$
\end_inset

及
\begin_inset Formula $y=0$
\end_inset

 同时代入
\begin_inset Formula $y'$
\end_inset

得
\begin_inset Formula $y'(0)=1$
\end_inset

,
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
注意
\series default
:由于
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的函数,
 该例中
\begin_inset Formula $e^{x}$
\end_inset

是以
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

为中间变量的关于
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的复合函数,因此对
\begin_inset Formula $e^{y}$
\end_inset

关于
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 求导应利用
\series bold
一元复合函数的求导方法
\series default
,
 
\begin_inset Formula $y'$
\end_inset

不能丢.
 另外,我们也应注意到,隐函数求导时,结果中可以含有
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

也可含有因变量
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

,
\series bold
因此求
\begin_inset Formula $y'(x_{0})$
\end_inset

时,应先将
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

代入方程
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)=0$
\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
求出笛卡尔叶形线
\series bold

\begin_inset Formula $x^{3}+y^{3}=6xy$
\end_inset


\series default
在点
\begin_inset Formula $(3,3)$
\end_inset

处的切线方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
解方程两边对
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

求导,可得
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+y^{2}y'=2x+2xy'$
\end_inset

,
 于是
\begin_inset Formula $y'=\frac{2y-x^{2}}{y^{2}-2x}$
\end_inset

 ,
 因此有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y'|_{(3,3)}=-1
\]

\end_inset

所以,切线方程为
\begin_inset Formula $y-3=-(x-3)$
\end_inset

,
 即
\begin_inset Formula $x+y=6$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+2xy-y^{2}=2x$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
\begin_inset Formula $2x+(2y+2xy')+2yy'=2$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
\begin_inset Formula $y^{2}$
\end_inset

复合函数先对
\begin_inset Formula $y^{2}$
\end_inset

求导，
再对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

求导
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
求
\begin_inset Formula $y=(1+x^{2})^{\sin x}$
\end_inset

的导数,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
对
\begin_inset Formula $y=(1+x^{2})^{\sin x}$
\end_inset

两边取对数,得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ln y=\sin x\ln(1+x^{2})
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
上式两边再求对
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的导数,得
\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{y}y'=\cos x\ln(1+x^{2})+\sin x\frac{1}{1+x^{2}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Solution
于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
y' & = & y(\cos x\ln(1+x^{2})+\sin x\frac{1}{1+x^{2}})\\
 &  & =(1+x^{2})^{\sin x}\cdot(\cos x\ln(1+x^{2})+\sin x\frac{1}{1+x^{2}})
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
注意
\series default
 该例是对
\series bold
显式函数求导
\series default
,
 因而要将结果中的因变量
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset


\series bold
代换掉
\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们也可以对幂指函数
\begin_inset Formula $y=f(x)$
\end_inset

两边取自然对数,
 将显式函数转变为隐函数,
 再用隐函数求导方法求出导数
\begin_inset Formula $y'$
\end_inset

,
 这种方法通常称为
\series bold
取对数求导法
\series default
.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
方法二:
 公式求隐函数的导数
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
采用多元复合函数求导的方法来找到隐函数的求导公式.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设方程
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)=0$
\end_inset

 确定了一元隐函数
\begin_inset Formula $y=f(x)$
\end_inset

,
 其中
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)$
\end_inset

具有一阶连续偏导数
\begin_inset Formula $F'_{x}$
\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset Formula $F'_{y}$
\end_inset

 且
\begin_inset Formula $F'_{y}\neq0$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)$
\end_inset

 是关于
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的复合函数,
 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 是中间变量,
 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 就是中间变量又是自变量.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
现在对方程
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)=0$
\end_inset

两边关于
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

求导,
 求多元复合函数求导法,
 可得 
\begin_inset Formula $F'_{x}\cdot\frac{\partial x}{\partial x}+F'_{y}\cdot\frac{\partial y}{\partial x}=F'_{x}+F'_{y}\cdot\frac{dy}{dx}=0$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
推导:
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,y)=0$
\end_inset

 即
\begin_inset Formula $F(x,F(x))=0$
\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其左端可以看做是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的一个复合函数，
求这个函数的全导数.得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial F}{\partial x}+\frac{\partial F}{\partial y}\frac{dy}{dx}=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{dy}{dx}=-\frac{\frac{\partial F}{\partial x}}{\frac{\partial F}{\partial y}}=-\frac{F'_{x}}{F'_{y}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
设
\begin_inset Formula $y=f(x)$
\end_inset

由方程
\begin_inset Formula $y=x\ln y$
\end_inset

确定，
求
\begin_inset Formula $y'$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset Formula $y'=-\frac{F'_{x}}{F'_{y}}=\frac{\ln y}{1-\frac{x}{y}}=\frac{y\ln y}{y-x}(y-x\neq0)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

