\begin_layout Theorem
(二元函数极值的必要条件) 设函数
\begin_inset Formula $z=f(x,y)$
\end_inset

在点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},y_{0})$
\end_inset

处的偏导数存在,
 且在点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},y_{0})$
\end_inset

取得极值,则它在该点处的偏导数必然为零,即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{x}^{'}(x_{0},y_{0})=0,f_{y}^{'}(x_{0},y_{0})=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
与一元函数类似,我们把满足方程组
\begin_inset Formula $\begin{cases}
f_{x}^{'}(x_{0},y_{0})= & 0\\
f_{y}^{'}(x_{0},y_{0})= & 0
\end{cases}$
\end_inset

的点
\begin_inset Formula $(x,y)$
\end_inset

称为二元函数
\begin_inset Formula $f(x,y)$
\end_inset

的
\series bold
驻点
\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
从定理可知,具有偏导数的函数的极值点必定是驻点,但函数的驻点不一定是
\series bold
极值点
\series default
.
