(二元函数极值的充分条件) 设函数 
\begin_inset Formula $z=f(x,y)$
\end_inset

在点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},y_{0})$
\end_inset

的某邻域内有二阶连续偏导数,且
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},y_{0})$
\end_inset

为函数的驻点,即
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{x}^{'}(x_{0},y_{0})=0,f_{y}^{'}(x_{0},y_{0})=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

