令
\begin_inset Formula $f_{xx}^{''}(x_{0},y_{0})=A$
\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{xy}^{''}(x_{0},y_{0})=B$
\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{yy}^{''}(x_{0},y_{0})=C$
\end_inset

,则
\begin_inset Formula $f(x,y)$
\end_inset

在点
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0},y_{0})$
\end_inset

处是否取得极值的条件如下:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
(1) 当
\begin_inset Formula $B^{2}-AC<0$
\end_inset

