\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
非齐次一阶差分方程的通解由 齐次解 和 特解 之和组成：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{n}=x_{n}^{(h)}+x_{n}^{(p)}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求齐次解 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
先求解对应的 齐次方程 ：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{n+1}=ax_{n}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其通解为：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{n}^{(h)}=Ca^{n}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中，

\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 是待定的常数，
由初值条件确定。

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求特解 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
特解 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{n}^{(p)}$
\end_inset

 取决于 
\begin_inset Formula $\ensuremath{b_{n}}$
\end_inset

的形式：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
若 
\begin_inset Formula $b_{n}=b$
\end_inset

 是常数，
设特解为
\begin_inset Formula $x_{n}^{(p)}=A$
\end_inset

，
代入方程：

\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A=aA+b
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
解得：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A=\frac{b}{1-a},\quad\text{(当 \ensuremath{a\neq1} 时)}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以特解是：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{n}^{(p)}=\frac{b}{1-a}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
若 
\begin_inset Formula $b_{n}$
\end_inset

 是某种特定的函数（如 
\begin_inset Formula $b_{n}=cn$
\end_inset

 或 
\begin_inset Formula $b_{n}=ca^{n}$
\end_inset

