x_{n+1}^{(h)}=2x_{n}^{(h)}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其通解：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{n}^{(h)}=C2^{n}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
求特解 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设特解为 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{n}^{(p)}=A$
\end_inset

，
代入方程：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A=2A+3
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
解得：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A=-3
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以特解是：

