\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{n}=C2^{n}-3
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由初值确定 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若已知 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}=1$
\end_inset

，
则：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
1=C2^{0}-3
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C=4
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
最终解：

