\begin_layout Standard
我们使用 链式法则：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{d}{dt}[\cos(\theta(t))]=-\sin\theta(t)\,\dot{\theta}(t)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{d}{dt}[\sin\theta(t)]=\cos\theta(t)\,\dot{\theta}(t)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以代入后得到：

