\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

呢？

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我们可以考虑差值
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
R_{n}(x)=f(x)-\left[f(0)+\frac{f'(0)}{1!}x+\frac{f''(0)}{2!}x^{2}+\cdots+\frac{f^{\{n\}}(0)}{n!}x^{n}+\cdots\right]
\]

\end_inset

可以证明，
当
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $(n+1)$
\end_inset

阶导数时,
 有
\begin_inset Formula $R_{n}(x)=\frac{f^{(n+1)}(\xi)}{(n+1)!}x^{n+1}$
\end_inset

,其中
\begin_inset Formula $\xi)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

之间.
 因此,
 若函数
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

在区间
\begin_inset Formula $(-R,R)$
\end_inset

内满足条件
\begin_inset Formula $\underset{n\rightarrow\infty}{\lim}R_{n}(x)=\underset{n\rightarrow\infty}{\lim}\frac{f^{(n+1)}(\xi)}{(n+1)!}x^{n+1}=0$
\end_inset

,
 则有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)=f(0)+\frac{f'(0)}{1!}x+\frac{f''(0)}{2!}x^{2}+\cdots+\frac{f^{\{n\}}(0)}{n!}x^{n}+\cdots
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
即
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

能在区间
\begin_inset Formula $(-R,R)$
\end_inset

内展开为麦克劳林级数,
