\begin_inset Formula $\ensuremath{A}$
\end_inset

是正交矩阵当且仅当它满足以下条件：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A^{T}=A^{-1}\Longleftrightarrow A^{T}A=AA^{T}=I
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

