\begin_layout Example
假设有二次型：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $Q(x_{1},x_{2})=2x_{1}^{2}+4x_{1}x_{2}+5x_{2}^{2}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对应的矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\ensuremath{A}$
\end_inset

为：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A=\begin{bmatrix}2 & 2\\
2 & 5
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
通过初等行列变换将矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\ensuremath{A}$
\end_inset

化为对角矩阵：

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}2 & 2\\
2 & 5
\end{bmatrix}\rightarrow\begin{bmatrix}6 & 0\\
0 & 1
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以标准型为：

