\end_inset

 是齐次的，
因为每一项（
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}$
\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset Formula $xy$
\end_inset

,
 
\begin_inset Formula $y^{2}$
\end_inset

）的次数都是 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

。

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $x^{3}+5xyz-2y^{2}z$
\end_inset

